{
  "stem": "323.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I woke up, and there was little bell, and a cross above my bed, and I just opened my bed, and all I said-- no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was out again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was unconscious again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She found me in the infirmary, eventually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't know where she was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in there, altogether, for six weeks before I could even walk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was set up at the camp by the British and volunteer Red Cross people from all over the world, like the French nuns.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then British soldiers came-- soldiers came came visiting us, and I had had some English in school, so I was able to talk English to them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they brought us chocolate and things like that we hadn't seen in I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that point, by the way, I weighed 78 pounds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I also found out that all the food was poisoned, and that the Germans had planned to give all this food to us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The British came too quickly, just before we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had poisoned the food in warehouses, and they were going to feed it to us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then that would have been a quick end, because everybody would have eaten it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they never got to do it, which was lucky.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Either they never got to do it-- maybe they never wanted to do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, sometimes people have a conscience when it comes down to the last-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know that somebody-- she was deported-- somebody informed, and says, listen, it's not what it seems to be.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's so and so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A prisoner, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think she stood trial, eventually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember her last name.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
